  "text": "Two studies on overweight showed interactions between neighbourhood SEP and individual characteristics. One study found out that an unexpected inverse association between a low neighbourhood SEP and overweight or obesity was only significant for men [CITATION_1] . A further study detected a negative association between a high neighbourhood SEP and BMI only for non-Hispanic whites [CITATION_2] .",
